{
  "stem": "25651.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was-- would buy these three rations from people who had dysentery, who had dysentery for three days and they hadn't eaten nothing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They could only eat white bread, because if they would eat this awful black bread-- the black bread was made with chestnuts.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was practically indigestible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But if you were hungry enough, you-- you ate the black bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were nights when I got a whole loaf of bread out of this profit, because I'd go back to the Krankenbau barrack, where I had access because I was the runner there, and I would sell black bread to dysentery patients who were already getting better.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I would give them two portions of black bread for one portion of white bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I'd go back and demand three portions of black bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So sometimes-- I did that about three times every evening, and I came away with a whole loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'd carry this to Milos.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- oh, there was another thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was offered to sleep in the Krankenbau, and I was given a porridge in the Krankenbau, which was a white soup.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was actually quite palatable, the porridge.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Much better than the soup in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The soup in the camp I could never eat, because it was made with rotten potatoes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it smelled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was made in these big beer barrels.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was transported in beer barrels, and the beer barrels got completely black on the inside from the soup rotting from day to day.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's why people caught dysentery, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a sort of rolling effect.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the fact that the ration went down, you know, because at first we got 1,500 calories.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
